Package: wb-python-service-template
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-jsonschema, python3-wb-common (>= 2.1.0~~)
Description: Template of a Python service for Wiren Board
 This package provides an template of a Python service for Wiren Board devices.
 It demonstrates how to create a service that interacts with the system and
 can be managed using standard tools.